cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.LG. 

This paper deals with text summarization algorithms and their evaluation from a new perspective of fairness. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also involves social groups and their representation, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.CY (Computers and Society). The use of algorithms and evaluation methods could also place the paper under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
